- if @has_user_profile

  .ui.top.attached.header Profile
  .ui.attached.segment
    h3.ui.dividing.header
      = @user.profile.name
    p
    | ここに自己紹介を書く予定です。
  .ui.attached.header Skills
  .ui.attached.segment
    .ui.two.column.devided.grid
      .ui.container
        - @user.profile.skills.each do |skill|
          .ui.basic.skill.button
            = "#{skill.name}"
    - if @user != current_user
      = link_to "スキルを推薦する",  new_user_profile_skill_path(@user, @profile), class: "ui green basic button"
  - if @user == current_user
    .ui.attached.header Edit
    .ui.attached.segment
      = link_to "Profileを編集する", edit_user_profile_path(@user), class: "ui button"


- else

  h1.ui.dividing.header
    | ユーザープロフィールが存在しません。
